Randgold & Exploration Considering ‘Dozens’ of Deals, Business Day Reports

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-04-07T04:53:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/randgold-exploration-considering-dozens-of-deals-business-day-reports.html
 Randgold & Exploration Ltd. is
considering “dozens” of potential deals which it says will
give shape to its future mining strategy, Business Day reported,
citing Chief Executive Officer Marais Steyn.  The company has about 180 million rand in cash and
outstanding claims running into billions of rand, the
Johannesburg-based newspaper said, citing Steyn.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  